Description: Modern Steam Authenticator for Linux
 A modern Steam Authenticator for Linux with 2FA code generation
 and trade confirmation support. Built with GTK4 and libadwaita
 for a native Linux desktop experience.
 .
 Features:
  - Generate Steam Guard 2FA codes
  - View and manage trade confirmations
  - Support for multiple Steam accounts
  - 8 beautiful themes
  - Import/export .maFile accounts
